title: QB Rankings: 11-20 + Preseason Highlights, Buckle Up! - Fantasy Football Podcast for 8/16
description:
The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode! On today’s fantasy football podcast, Andy, Mike, and Jason countdown mid to late round QBs for the 2021 season! Find out which players are the best values that you can get late in your fantasy football drafts. Plus, reactions to the Week 1 Preseason action! Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for August 16th, 2021.
  
 Dominate your fantasy football draft with the 2021 Ultimate Draft Kit -- get the Draft Analyzer with the UDK+
  
 (03:20) - Preseason Week 1 Takeaways
 (07:50) - NFL News
 (11:45) - Quarterback Rankings Part Two
 (14:15) - Jalen Hurts
 (18:00) - Taysom Hill / Jameis Winston
 (25:35) - Kirk Cousins
 (31:00) - Matt Ryan
 (33:00) - Matthew Stafford
 (38:55) - Joe Burrow
 (41:45) - Trevor Lawrence
 (45:25) - Ben Roethlisberger
 (48:20) - Ryan Fitzpatrick
 (51:50) - Baker Mayfield
 (52:30) -  Tua Tagovailoa, Sam Darnold
 (54:40) - Trey Lance, Justin Fields
